{"tid":1551010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日會集會遊行嘅 入一入黎","createTime":"2019-09-07T20:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T22:16:10.000Z","uid":140432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90feb9d3420a8962a5632e6cccc4c7c79a787fb3","tid":1551010,"uid":140432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:05:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同我聽到識背為至！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日一齊唱<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港國歌</span>！</span><br />\n<br />\n一齊唱《<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span>》<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">何以 這土地 淚再流</span><br />\nIn angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">何以 令眾人 亦憤恨</span><br />\nWith rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透</span><br />\nWe rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">盼自由 歸於 這裡</span><br />\nAs we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">何以 這恐懼 抹不走</span><br />\nWith eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">何以 為信念 從沒退後</span><br />\nIn faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透</span><br />\nOur flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">建自由 光輝 香港</span><br />\nFree this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜</span><br />\nStars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲</span><br />\nStorms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">捍自由</span><br />\nWe shall strike<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">來齊集這裡 </span><br />\nThis perilous night<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">來全力抗對</span><br />\nDetermined to fight<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot;</span><br />\nWith hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黎明來到 要光復 這香港</span><br />\nGlory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同行兒女 為正義 時代革命</span><br />\nFreedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽</span><br />\nLiberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我願 榮光 歸香港 </span><br />\n Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"26a03ac167aafe4e0923c6cbf87d2305bbf67596","tid":1551010,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:06:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f879a4d896bedffc1aa9066def8653e4f29bd48","ti